{"id":262035,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-《民生观察》负责人刘飞跃被警方带走后/","date":"2012-11-09T05:45:58Z","modified":"2012-11-09T05:45:58Z","title":"维权网 | 《民生观察》负责人刘飞跃被警方带走后失踪两天（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员东建报道）湖北省随州市民生观察工作室的负责人刘飞跃，自本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点被随州市国保从家中带走后，手机一直处于无法接通状态，至今已失踪两天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1akoceHoneY/UJyBIk_DjXI/AAAAAAAATMU/jok2UDrmkG8/s1600/%E5%88%98%E9%A3%9E%E8%B7%83.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1akoceHoneY/UJyBIk_DjXI/AAAAAAAATMU/jok2UDrmkG8/s1600/%E5%88%98%E9%A3%9E%E8%B7%83.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自刘飞跃被警方带走后，本网信息员曾数次拨打其手机，都提示为“呼叫的用户已启用手机秘书服务”，目前刘飞跃是否被强制旅游或被羁押某处都不得而知。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>《民生观察》网站自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日至今尚未更新。作为民生观察工作室的负责人，刘飞跃多年来坚持关注中国大陆的侵权个案，尤其关注被精神病患者和民办教师的权利问题。近几年来，被断网、软禁在家无法出门、被强制旅游、被强迫失踪、遭受殴打等一系列的迫害，已成为刘飞跃的生存常态。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8150155690669329673?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,